---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '../../components/Button.astro';
import QuoteBlock from '../../components/QuoteBlock.astro';
import SectionDivider from '../../components/SectionDivider.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Magnalia" description="The journal of Catholic cultural renewal in Canada. Essays, art, and letters from leading Catholic thinkers.">

  <!-- Section 1: Hero -->
  <section class="section section--dark magnalia-hero">
    <div class="container magnalia-hero__inner">
      <div class="magnalia-hero__text">
        <p class="label text-gold">The Journal of Catholic Cultural Renewal in Canada</p>
        <h1 class="magnalia-hero__title display">Magnalia</h1>
        <p class="magnalia-hero__subtitle"><em>Great and wonderful things</em></p>
        <p class="magnalia-hero__body">
          Magnalia brings together the finest Catholic writing, scholarship, and art in Canada. Each
          60-page issue features original essays from leading Catholic thinkers, letters from the field,
          and beautiful visual art. Published twice yearly by the Gregory the Great Institute.
        </p>
        <div class="magnalia-hero__ctas">
          <Button href="/magnalia/subscribe" variant="secondary">Subscribe to Magnalia</Button>
          <a href="#sample" class="magnalia-hero__link">Read a Sample →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="magnalia-hero__cover">
        <img src="/images/branding/Magnalia_Cover.jpg" alt="Magnalia Journal — Issue One" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: What's Inside -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container inside-section">
      <div class="inside-section__main">
        <h2>Inside Issue One</h2>
        <div class="toc">
          <div class="toc__item">
            <span class="toc__type label">Essay</span>
            <p class="toc__title">The Recovery of Sunday</p>
            <p class="toc__author">Dr. Ryan N.S. Topping</p>
          </div>
          <div class="toc__item">
            <span class="toc__type label">Letter</span>
            <p class="toc__title">From the Western Front: Catholic Life in Alberta</p>
            <p class="toc__author">Victor Carpay</p>
          </div>
          <div class="toc__item">
            <span class="toc__type label">Essay</span>
            <p class="toc__title">Classical Education and the Canadian Imagination</p>
            <p class="toc__author">Dr. Celene Sidloski</p>
          </div>
          <div class="toc__item">
            <span class="toc__type label">Review</span>
            <p class="toc__title">Reading Pieper in a Distracted Age</p>
            <p class="toc__author">Dr. Joseph Woodard</p>
          </div>
          <div class="toc__item">
            <span class="toc__type label">Essay</span>
            <p class="toc__title">Vocations and the Canadian Church: A Statistical Portrait</p>
            <p class="toc__author">Mark Ingham</p>
          </div>
          <div class="toc__item">
            <span class="toc__type label">Interview</span>
            <p class="toc__title">On Building Culture in Times of Upheaval</p>
            <p class="toc__author">Fr. Michael Bombak with Ryan Topping</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <QuoteBlock
          quote="The renewal of Catholic culture in Canada will not come from institutions alone. It will come from the lived encounter between faith, beauty, and the daily work of forming souls."
          attribution="From the Editor"
          title="Dr. Ryan N.S. Topping"
          variant="light"
        />
      </div>
      <aside class="inside-section__sidebar">
        <div class="issue-meta">
          <p class="issue-meta__label label text-gold">Issue One</p>
          <dl class="issue-meta__list">
            <dt>Pages</dt>
            <dd>60</dd>
            <dt>Published</dt>
            <dd>Winter 2026</dd>
            <dt>Contributors</dt>
            <dd>8</dd>
            <dt>Format</dt>
            <dd>Print (60 pages)</dd>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider />

  <!-- Section 3: Sample Content -->
  <section class="section" id="sample">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sample-article">
        <p class="label text-gold">Sample from Issue One</p>
        <h2 class="sample-article__title">The Recovery of Sunday</h2>
        <p class="sample-article__byline">By <strong>Dr. Ryan N.S. Topping</strong> · 12 min read</p>

        <div class="prose">
          <p>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt
            ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. In the West, we have largely forgotten what Sunday means.
            Not merely as a day of rest — though it is that — but as the day that gives meaning to all
            the other days. Josef Pieper understood this when he wrote that leisure is the basis of culture.
          </p>
          <p>
            Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea
            commodo consequat. The Christian Sunday is not the weekend. It is the Lord's Day — the day
            when creation is renewed, when the Eucharist is celebrated, when the community gathers not
            for productivity but for worship. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit
            esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.
          </p>
          <blockquote class="sample-article__pullquote">
            <p>"To celebrate Sunday means to celebrate the world's birthday — to stand before creation and say: it is very good."</p>
          </blockquote>
          <p>
            Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit
            anim id est laborum. What would it mean for Canadian Catholic culture if we recovered this
            ancient practice? If Sunday became, once again, the day that formed our weeks, our families,
            our communities? Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium
            doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam.
          </p>
          <p>
            Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia
            consequuntur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt. The recovery of Sunday
            is not nostalgia. It is a prophetic act — a refusal to reduce human life to the logic of
            production and consumption. It is the claim that we are made for more than work...
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="sample-article__cta">
          <p class="sample-article__cta-text">Subscribe to read the full issue and future editions.</p>
          <Button href="/magnalia/subscribe" variant="primary">Subscribe to Magnalia</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: Contributors -->
  <section class="section section--linen">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="label text-gold">Who Writes Magnalia</p>
        <h2>Our Contributors</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="contributors-grid">
        <div class="contributor-card">
          <img src="/images/people/Ryan-Topping-headshot.jpg" alt="Dr. Ryan Topping" class="contributor-card__photo" />
          <h3 class="contributor-card__name">Dr. Ryan N.S. Topping</h3>
          <p class="contributor-card__credentials">DPhil (Oxford) · 11 books</p>
          <p class="contributor-card__bio">Executive Director. Catholic education and cultural philosophy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contributor-card">
          <img src="/images/people/Catherine-Renneberg-headshot.jpg" alt="Catherine Renneberg" class="contributor-card__photo" />
          <h3 class="contributor-card__name">Dr. Celene Sidloski</h3>
          <p class="contributor-card__credentials">Fellow · Saskatoon</p>
          <p class="contributor-card__bio">Classical education and Canadian Catholic intellectual life.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contributor-card">
          <div class="contributor-card__photo contributor-card__photo--placeholder"></div>
          <h3 class="contributor-card__name">Dr. Joseph Woodard</h3>
          <p class="contributor-card__credentials">Fellow · Calgary</p>
          <p class="contributor-card__bio">Ethics, bioethics, and Catholic social thought.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contributor-card">
          <div class="contributor-card__photo contributor-card__photo--placeholder"></div>
          <h3 class="contributor-card__name">Mark Ingham</h3>
          <p class="contributor-card__credentials">Fellow · Barry's Bay · PhD Cand.</p>
          <p class="contributor-card__bio">Vocations research and Canadian Catholic demographics.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section-footer">
        <Button href="/magnalia/contributors" variant="tertiary">Meet All Contributors →</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider />

  <!-- Section 5: Subscription Options Preview -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Read Magnalia</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="sub-tiers">
        <div class="sub-tier">
          <h3 class="sub-tier__name">Single Copy</h3>
          <p class="sub-tier__price">$45</p>
          <p class="sub-tier__desc">Try a single issue of Magnalia.</p>
          <Button href="/magnalia/subscribe" variant="secondary" size="small">Order a Copy</Button>
        </div>
        <div class="sub-tier sub-tier--featured">
          <p class="sub-tier__badge label">Most Popular</p>
          <h3 class="sub-tier__name">Annual Subscription</h3>
          <p class="sub-tier__price">$80<span class="sub-tier__period">/year</span></p>
          <p class="sub-tier__desc">Two issues per year. The standard for Friends of Magnalia.</p>
          <Button href="/magnalia/subscribe" variant="primary" size="small">Subscribe</Button>
        </div>
        <div class="sub-tier">
          <h3 class="sub-tier__name">Magnalia Patron</h3>
          <p class="sub-tier__price">$500<span class="sub-tier__period">/year</span></p>
          <p class="sub-tier__desc">Subscription + named recognition + quarterly Q&A with the editor.</p>
          <Button href="/magnalia/subscribe" variant="secondary" size="small">Become a Patron</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="sub-student-note">Student & seminarian rate: $30/year · Family rate: $50/year · <a href="/magnalia/subscribe">View all options →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6: Magnalia Letter Cross-sell -->
  <section class="section section--dark">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center; max-width: 600px;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--color-text-on-dark); margin-bottom: 12px;">Between Issues</h2>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(245,239,229,0.8); margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.7;">
        Stay connected with the Magnalia Letter — a free monthly essay from the Institute, plus event invitations
        and reading recommendations.
      </p>
      <form class="newsletter-section__form" action="#" method="POST" style="justify-content: center;">
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email address" class="newsletter-inline-input" required />
        <button type="submit" class="newsletter-inline-btn">Subscribe Free</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .magnalia-hero__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-component);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .magnalia-hero__title {
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark);
    margin: 8px 0 4px;
  }

  .magnalia-hero__subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.75);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .magnalia-hero__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .magnalia-hero__ctas {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .magnalia-hero__link {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.6);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .magnalia-hero__link:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .magnalia-hero__cover img {
    max-width: 360px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: block;
    transform: rotate(-2deg);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .magnalia-hero__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Inside Section */
  .inside-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-component);
  }

  .inside-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .toc {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-component);
  }

  .toc__item {
    padding: 16px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.1);
  }

  .toc__type {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .toc__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .toc__author {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .issue-meta {
    background-color: var(--color-linen);
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.08);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .issue-meta__label {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .issue-meta__list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 8px 16px;
  }

  .issue-meta__list dt {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-gray);
  }

  .issue-meta__list dd {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-navy);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .inside-section {
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Sample Article */
  .sample-article {
    max-width: var(--max-prose-width);
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .sample-article__title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 8px 0 12px;
  }

  .sample-article__byline {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.1);
  }

  .sample-article__pullquote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-gold);
    padding-left: 24px;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .sample-article__pullquote p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .sample-article__cta {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--color-gold);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .sample-article__cta-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  /* Contributors */
  .contributors-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .contributor-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 24px 16px;
  }

  .contributor-card__photo {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .contributor-card__photo--placeholder {
    background-color: var(--color-ivory);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .contributor-card__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .contributor-card__credentials {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .contributor-card__bio {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .contributors-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  /* Subscription Tiers */
  .sub-tiers {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .sub-tier {
    background-color: var(--color-linen);
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.1);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 28px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .sub-tier--featured {
    border: 2px solid var(--color-gold);
  }

  .sub-tier__badge {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .sub-tier__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .sub-tier__price {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .sub-tier__period {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-gray);
  }

  .sub-tier__desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .sub-tiers {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .sub-student-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .sub-student-note a {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .sub-student-note a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* Inline newsletter in dark section */
  .newsletter-inline-input {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    background: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.2);
    border-radius: 3px;
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark);
    outline: none;
    min-width: 240px;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .newsletter-inline-input:focus {
    border-color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .newsletter-inline-input::placeholder {
    color: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.35);
  }

  .newsletter-inline-btn {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background-color: var(--color-gold);
    color: var(--color-navy);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 3px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .newsletter-inline-btn:hover {
    background-color: #a08638;
  }

  /* Shared */
  .section--linen {
    background-color: var(--color-linen);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-component);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .section-footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-component);
  }
</style>
